\frac{\sqrt5}{5}
\frac{\sqrt{5} + \sqrt{5-\frac2n}}{\sqrt{5} + \sqrt{5-\frac2n}}
n
2\sqrt{x}
x=5
 \lim_{n\to +\infty}n\cdot\left(\sqrt5-\sqrt{5-\frac2n}\right)=\lim_{n\to +\infty}2\cdot\frac{\sqrt{5-\frac2n}-\sqrt5}{-\frac{2}{n}}=2\lim_{h\to 0}\frac{\sqrt{5+h}-\sqrt5}{h}=2 (\sqrt{x})'_{x=5}\\=2\cdot\frac{1}{2}\cdot \frac{1}{\sqrt{5}}=\frac{1}{\sqrt{5}}. 
